platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: 不准蛇王！大量的工作等著你，只有完成所有編程才可以升職、保飯碗。
想要升職保飯碗，就得運用邏輯思考，寫程式解開老闆給的不同任務。

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 自編程式解謎 博取升職機會
ロジックパズルに挑戦しよう
以編程邏輯解謎 保住飯碗

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Being able to write computer code is a supremely useful talent, but learning the basics can be a tough, tedious slog. Human Resource Machine wraps computer logic fundamentals inside a wonderful, whimsical puzzle game, full of cartoon conveyer belts and demanding managers. It’s so much fun you might not realise how much knowledge you’re soaking up.
